    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1RenderCallback" kindref="compound">RenderCallback</ref> is used by the direct rendering feature and allows injecting custom render code (using native API such as GL directly) into the DALi rendering stream. The <ref refid="classDali_1_1RenderCallback" kindref="compound">RenderCallback</ref> will be executed within own context (unless native API is context-less) to maintain state separation from DALi render state.</para>
<para>The class wraps <ref refid="classDali_1_1CallbackBase" kindref="compound">CallbackBase</ref> object ensuring its type-safe assignment</para>
<para>@SINCE_2_1.14 </para>
